- System improvements to base SURTASS-E RPED capability based on operational feedback and COTF Quick Reaction Assessment (OT&E).  Improvements are necessary to address shortcomings in the SURTASS-E prototype.
- System improvements to address COTF cybersecurity test findings.  Improvements are necessary to ensure continuity of operations and prevent compromise by internal and external threats.
- Upgrade SURTASS-E capability to support military crew (MILCREW) manning.  Base SURTASS-E capability does not support MILCREW manning, which is necessary to support planned Fleet operational plans;
